{"tid":2360931,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"大批特朗普支持者轉用MeWe導致系統一度無法負荷","createTime":"2021-01-10T08:18:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-10T18:19:23.000Z","uid":20933,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fd833f6767ada69c6b847d0318f5ab86ad5bf9e6","tid":2360931,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T08:18:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://stream.881903.com/public/0508dec9d24978c3c3223fe5755bebab/2021/01/fab8957ec25168ddded79a4ce8cdae28.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstream.881903.com%2Fpublic%2F0508dec9d24978c3c3223fe5755bebab%2F2021%2F01%2Ffab8957ec25168ddded79a4ce8cdae28.jpg&h=3e140582&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n被視為美國總統特朗普支持者陣地的社交平台程式「Parler」，相繼被蘋果、Google及亞馬遜封殺後，大批用戶轉到另一個新興社交平台「MeWe」，導致「MeWe」的系統一度死機。「MeWe」解釋，最近突然有大量新成員加入，並上載相片及照片，導致系統無法負荷，暫時回復正常。 <br />\n<br />\n「Parler」深受保守派歡迎。近日，因為Twitter同Facebook打擊散播錯誤訊息和煽動暴力的帖文，大批特朗普支持者轉用「Parler」。但Google及蘋果公司把「Parler」從應用程式商店下架，認為「Parler」未能足夠監管發言，出現過多鼓勵暴力和犯罪的帖文。亞馬遜就宣布，不再為社交平台程式「Parler」提供雲端服務。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/international/2374166\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Finternational%2F2374166&d=3UqZ%2FPYEUq8PtOmaimGdDZnDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=b8bd67f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/international/2374166</a>"},{"pid":"ec981f3893e42b2105a60ff479c123e18f8b55a9","tid":2360931,"uid":128211,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"fd833f6767ada69c6b847d0318f5ab86ad5bf9e6","tid":2360931,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T08:18:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://stream.881903.com/public/0508dec9d24978c3c3223fe5755bebab/2021/01/fab8957ec25168ddded79a4ce8cdae28.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstream.881903.com%2Fpublic%2F0508dec9d24978c3c3223fe5755bebab%2F2021%2F01%2Ffab8957ec25168ddded79a4ce8cdae28.jpg&h=3e140582&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n被視為美國總統特朗普支持者陣地的社交平台程式「Parler」，相繼被蘋果、Google及亞馬遜封殺後，大批用戶轉到另一個新興社交平台「MeWe」，導致「MeWe」的系統一度死機。「MeWe」解釋，最近突然有大量新成員加入，並上載相片及照片，導致系統無法負荷，暫時回復正常。 <br />\n<br />\n「Parler」深受保守派歡迎。近日，因為Twitter同Facebook打擊散播錯誤訊息和煽動暴力的帖文，大批特朗普支持者轉用「Parler」。但Google及蘋果公司把「Parler」從應用程式商店下架，認為「Parler」未能足夠監管發言，出現過多鼓勵暴力和犯罪的帖文。亞馬遜就宣布，不再為社交平台程式「Parler」提供雲端服務。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/international/2374166\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Finternational%2F2374166&d=3UqZ%2FPYEUq8PtOmaimGdDZnDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=b8bd67f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/international/2374166</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T17:57:03.000Z","msg":"衣家仲Lag緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"013812bcde376119348205c44a2ffbf5eb92bbfe","tid":2360931,"uid":61755,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T17:58:49.000Z","msg":"咪過一排又死死地氣番去FB<br />\n2個月前都係咁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7104fabe0ee6cf7b3511467e43bbbad9f0b6087","tid":2360931,"uid":1643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T18:19:23.000Z","msg":"香港人隨時又要搵新 social network<br />\nmewe 可能隨時好似 parler 咁比 apple, google 同 amazon 迫害,<br />\n仲要 mewe 冇 mobile web version"}]}